oidc-agent is an installed application that only runs on the users machine. 
oidc-agent only communicates with the OpenID Provider the user intends to.
No data is sent to third parties. 
All data is stored locally on the user's machine in an encrypted way.
Logs are only written to the user's system log.

This oidc-agent instance will only be used for personal use of the user
registering the client_id/client_secret of this instance. It will not be
made available to other users.

The client_id/client_secret will remain on personal computers under
control of the user requesting credentials.

